{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerSmsNumber:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerSmsNumber:","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","title":"registerSmsNumber:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerSmsNumber:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerSmsNumber:"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers an SMS number for SMS messaging campaigns."}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerSmsNumber:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"number"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"number","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The phone number in E.164 international format."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Associates a phone number with the current device for SMS marketing campaigns."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This enables omnichannel messaging where users can receive communications via"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"both push notifications and SMS."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The phone number must be in E.164 international format:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Start with ‘+’ followed by country code"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"No spaces, dashes, or parentheses","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Examples: “+14155551234” (US), “+447911123456” (UK), “+491711234567” (Germany)"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Register SMS during phone verification flow:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class PhoneVerificationController {","","    func verifyPhoneNumber(_ phoneNumber: String, code: String,","                          completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","","        APIClient.shared.verifyCode(phone: phoneNumber, code: code) { [weak self] result in","            switch result {","            case .success:","                let normalizedNumber = self?.normalizeToE164(phoneNumber) ?? phoneNumber","                Pushwoosh.configure.registerSmsNumber(normalizedNumber)","","                Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                    \"phone_verified\": true,","                    \"sms_opted_in\": true,","                    \"phone_country\": self?.extractCountryCode(from: normalizedNumber) ?? \"\"","                ])","","                completion(.success(()))","","            case .failure(let error):","                completion(.failure(error))","            }","        }","    }","","    private func normalizeToE164(_ phone: String) -> String {","        let digits = phone.components(separatedBy: CharacterSet.decimalDigits.inverted).joined()","        return phone.hasPrefix(\"+\") ? \"+\\(digits)\" : \"+1\\(digits)\"","    }","","    private func extractCountryCode(from e164: String) -> String {","        \/\/ Extract country code from E.164 format","        guard e164.hasPrefix(\"+\") else { return \"\" }","        let countryCodeLength = e164.count > 12 ? 2 : (e164.count > 11 ? 1 : 1)","        return String(e164.dropFirst().prefix(countryCodeLength))","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registersmsnumber:"]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/registerSmsNumber:":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerSmsNumber:"}],"title":"registerSmsNumber:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerSmsNumber:"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers an SMS number for SMS messaging campaigns."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registersmsnumber:","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerSmsNumber:","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore"}}}